name: Fathead
overview: Fathead, LLC provides sports and entertainment wall graphics. The company offers fatheads, which include national football league (NFL) players, national basketball association (NBA) players, national association for stock car auto racing (NASCAR) cars, NASCAR drivers, NASCAR numbers, NBA logos, national hockey league (NHL) players, base ball players, NHL logos, NFL helmets, and base ball logos fatheads. It also offers college sports helmets, college sports logos, cow boys cheerleaders, wicked wrestling entertainment, action sports, tennis, military, soccer, fatheads, batman, superman, star wars, family guys, the simpsons, sports illustrated swimsuits, spider-man 3, fantastic four, hulks, X-men, hannah montana, and high school musical fatheads. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in Livonia, Michigan.
